onecardmultiplenumbers service in mainland china hong kong macau and taiwan for over a decade and planning to merge with oversea mnos through acquisition in order to qualify for global roaming skytone business introduction         skytone is a new type creative integrated telecom roaming service which is based on the group’s years experience on one card multiple numbers service and combined with new era mobile internet technology by working with the oversea operators the group can provide a more convenient and cheaper roaming service with higher quality to the users                 taking the advantage of casim card’s onecardmultiplenumbers feature the skytone service provided by the group could tackle two biggest issues of high roaming charges and difficult local sim card purchase with core technologies such as writing sim card over the air by app ca authentication and encryption and goip etc the group has created a new generation of roaming product           meanwhile skytone is compatible with all kinds of network meeting the strong needs of cdma users who want to travel aboard business patterns         other than chinahk telecom’s  imsi the group works with other mno and mvno mainly by manufacturing normal sim card and acquiring output file data from the card manufacturer and then writing it into casim card by skytone app         oversea casim users roaming in hong kongmainland china writing chinahk telecom’s  imsi or other imsi from our cooperated china operators into casim card to add hong kongmainland china phone numbers         hong kongmainland china users roaming aboard writing output file data from the local mnomvno by skytone app to add local phone numbers skytone service apps         the core app of the skytone system is directtx app                 the directel exclusive technology can register sim card into the network remotely through casim and goip device which does not need to alter operator’s network when one of the user’s numbers was called including voice and sms follow me will forward it to the user’s phone in the roaming location via directel app or general gsm module the user would not need to pay for the call forward or idd fees with valueadded service apps featuring traveling and so on users can purchase more nontelecom products                 related links directeltx app           with valueadded service apps featuring traveling and so on users can purchase more nontelecom products           skytone                 with skytone app skytone product combines with casim casim users gathered by all channels could write numbers into their casim card over the air by themselves           skytone app can encrypt or decrypt card data such as imsi and ki and then write them safely into the casim card with the skytone system single number users such as mainland china users could upgrade to multiple numbers users         related links：skytone app  ota（over the app） briefdirectel holdings reports qtrly loss of hk million  reuters discover thomson reutersfinancialgovernment solutionslegalreuters news agencyrisk management solutionstax  accountingblog answers oninnovation  thomson reutersdirectory of siteslogincontactsupport months agobriefdirectel holdings reports qtrly loss of hk millionrbipolicyreviewtechnologyspecialreportstopnewsthewiderimagecompanyresultsslideshowssectionsbusinessmarketsindiaworldtechcommentarybreakingviewssport  lifepicturesreuters tvdiscover thomson reutersfinancialgovernment solutionslegalreuters news agencyrisk management solutionstax  accountingblog answers oninnovation  thomson reutersdirectory of siteslogincontactsupportfeaturedearningsioc firstquarter profit falls  percent but beats estimatescultureover half of indias languages may die out in  yearsworldtrump blames congress for alltime low in russia tiespicturesreuters tveditionunited statesafricaamérica latinaعربيargentinabrasilcanadadeutschlandespañafranceindiaitaliaméxicoроссияunited kingdomunited statestechnology media and telec